DEFINE: FST_WSR_PROB   1                                                        # Probability semiring
DEFINE: FST_WSR_LOG    2                                                        # Log semiring
DEFINE: FST_WSR_TROP   3                                                        # Tropical semiring

## Defines - Graph iterator modes / unit change flags
